# === Docs: Three-tier structure ===
# Ignore internal and private docs, keep public un-ignored
docs/internal/
docs/private/
docs/README.md

# === Public docs (un-ignored) ===
# These are the ONLY docs visible in public releases
!docs/public/
!docs/public/*.md
!docs/public/guides/
!docs/public/changelogs/
!docs/public/community/
!docs/public/design/
!docs/public/misc/

# === Temporary ===
tmp/
temp_venv/
scratch/
wm
.restructure_backups/whitemagic-legacy-v21.0.0.tar.gz
